social_posts.post_text: By far the biggest largemouth bass I’ve ever seen caught in person..I still can’t believe it 👀😂 (I’ll be heading back to this lake during the spawn in March and I believe we will break the lake record when we go 🤯) stay tuned
I’m very sad to report that Timmy (my pet bass) has died tragically 😭😭 we are conducting a full investigation as we speak and awaiting autopsy reports. New vid is live on YouTube #petbass

It’s not the MONSTER buck that I wanted..but in a lot of ways it’s better that it happened this way. This deer season I learned just how difficult trophy buck hunting (and just regular deer hunting) can be. It challenged me. But, through all the failure and heartbreak, we persevered!! We documented the entire process on the newest YouTube vid that just went live if you wanna check out the process 👍👊 thank you to every single one of you guys that encouraged me along the way 🙏🙏 @buxhunting @andrewjamesking @justinmueller__ @common_man_outdoors #hunting #deer
Such an intense style of hunting during the rut!! This was my first full deer season but it definitely won’t be my last💪 #deer #deerhunting #whitetail

Had an epic fishing day on the Chatahoochie River recently. We caught TWO of the biggest hybrid bass I’ve ever caught (my biggest, an 8 Lber that we didn’t picture). Andrew shattered his pb with an almost 9 Lber!! All on Alabama rigs. It’s safe to say that river has a special place in my heart!! @andrewjamesking @justinmueller__

So excited to finally get my hands on some new @googansquad baitcasting reels and put ‘em to the test on some big Texas bass!! Big thanks to @lmbassman for letting us crash his lake again 😂🙏👊 check out the new vid on YouTube for a chance to win one before they are released to the public 👀
Texas crappie are built different 👀 I caught my new 2.2 lb PB crappie (on the new @googanbaits Bumpin Bug) and then cooked it up for the boys #fishtacos

Took my oldest daughter Lily fishing for the first time recently. I’d highly recommend it 🥹❤️ so proud of my girl!! Vid coming soon. Have a great weekend everyone 👊 @this_mommy_lifts thanks for the sweet action pics dear 😘 #fishing

I’ve gone from weighing up to 260lbs and feeling like crap (swipe right) to now under 220 and feeling great for over 18 months now. Best part is I’ve been able to cultivate a new lifestyle (centered around drinking water, eating more wild game, and daily intermittent fasting) that I can stick to for years to come. Not bad for a YouTube fisherman 😏. It also doesn’t hurt that I have @this_mommy_lifts to always motivate me through her own dedication to fitness 😍🥰 Have a great weekend folks!! Live your best life 💪👊
What can I say..I’m not a fan of the danger noodles 🐍 (notice the manly scream I used to scare the snake away 🫠)
Another day..another E-bike crash 🤷🏼‍♂️🤦‍♂️ #ilikegoingfast

We had the honor and pleasure of fishing with a true OG fishing YouTube LEGEND 🙌🏼🙌🏼🙌🏼 Richard Gene the Fishing Machine thank you sir for showing us around Lake Guntersville and showing us a thing or two 👊🙏 (vid coming soon on YouTube) @andrewjamesking

My heart aches a little each day thinking about the uniformed brothers and sisters that have been lost over time. Not just through combat, but also suicide and overdose 😢 So let us all remember and celebrate all those brave souls who made the ultimate sacrifice on this Memorial Day . There are too many to name in a single post, so I’ll stick to my brothers: 
Brian Nemocek
Charles Schwartz
Wes Harris
Jimmy Hall
Anthony Nunn 
Noel Foster
Nolan Barnham 
Jeremy Summers 

I will never forget you. 

#memorialday

I always thought the Grand Canyon was overrated…boy was I wrong!! Had the pleasure recently of being invited out to beautiful Utah by @polarisinc to test drive their new ATV (XPEDITION). Over 100+ miles of desert and mountain trails PLUS rooftop tent camping overnight at the base of a huge mountain!! Then a quick visit to that big ole Grand Canyon to top it off. Simply incredible scenery out west 👏😮‍💨 the full video is on YouTube if you want a little closer look at the vehicle and my experience 😎 Have a great and safe weekend everybody!! #atv #camping

This is the first Father’s Day since my dad passed away last October, making today a little bittersweet. I’ve missed my dad every single day since he left. But if I could talk to him today I KNOW he’d tell me not to be saddened by loss, but to be thankful for what I have. I am thankful. Im thankful I get to be a dad myself to 2 wild girls and a stepdad to one cool boy 😎 My dad helped shape me as a man and becoming a dad myself cemented in my mind just how important dads are to their kids ☺️ Happy Father’s Day to all the dads out there 🍻 #fathersday

This new 52QT Ultra-Light Wheeled Cooler from @rticoutdoors is gonna be my new best friend this summer! It keeps our drinks cold for longer and is 30% lighter than other wheeled coolers. All while being ultra capable with off road wheels!! This thing is seriously the best cooler I’ve ever owned 👍👌

#RTICOutdoors #RTICPartner

Performing a fish rescue is BY FAR one of the most satisfying things I’ve done as an outdoorsman. Normally we as fisherman spend countless hours simply trying to FIND the fish..let alone how long it takes to actually catch them once you find them. But in these rare instances you know where the fish are, they’re trapped..and slowly dying. We were lucky enough to save this 5lber (along with hundreds of smaller fish) along the way. She was living in about 8 inches of water/mud when I netted her out there. Another few hours and these fish would have been done for ☠️ Enjoy your weekend folks!! #fishrescue #fishing

3 years, 5 months, and 12 days. That’s how long it’s been since I set my previous PB largemouth bass mark at 9 lbs 11 oz in Mexico (February 2020). This time it happened not too far away in Rising Star Texas. I’ll probably have to wait awhile before I break it again 😂 This beast weighed in at 12 lbs even 😳 by far the biggest bass I’ve ever hooked..let alone landed!! The @googansquad Grande Klutch claims another double digit at L & M Lake. The excitement I felt when that bass finally ended up in the net was indescribable. If you want to see a play by play of the fish catch go check out the new vid I just dropped on YouTube (you won’t believe how I caught it 😂) Big shout out to @lmbassman for always welcoming myself and @andrewjamesking out to his place to fish and film 🙏 (big shoutout to @bledsome for that intense landing job 😰😂) #newpb #trophybass

This is what a couple of bonafide tournament champions look like 🏆😂 (not bad for a Thursday night derby on the River) Me and @loganfishing.fr won the tournament with a little over 11 lbs on 3 fish and was fortunate to catch our big fish on a frog & it was epic!! #tournament #fishing

I’d like to wish a very special happy birthday to @this_mommy_lifts on this 6th day of November 😘You put up with a lot of shit being married to me and being a mother to these wild kids, but I promise you our lives would be meaningless without you in it❤️ (I look like such a dope taking pictures w/ my wife because I got so damn lucky ending up as your husband, and I’m just enjoying the he’ll out of it 😊) Happy birthday, my dear, and I love you.
